Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.26,0:00:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱菈  龙卷风里面…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.60,0:00:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.72,0:00:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是龙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.30,0:00:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在动！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.09,0:00:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎  艾莉莎！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.09,0:00:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎  要过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.43,0:00:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫兵  卫兵在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.77,0:00:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着王宫去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.91,0:00:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.08,0:02:17.87,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,1500)\pos(258,568)\blur2}各自的意念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有来王宫避难的人就放进来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.19,0:02:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.01,0:02:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.27,0:02:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.40,0:02:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太危险了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.02,0:02:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷  你有什么办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.41,0:02:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱险了么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.54,0:02:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带来毁灭和死亡的不详象征  龙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.57,0:02:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说莱菈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只龙也是污秽造成的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.40,0:03:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.88,0:03:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在还不敢相信自己的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙竟然真的出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.71,0:03:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你拯救了瑞迪雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷  你看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导师保护了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导师大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.54,0:03:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  请冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.00,0:03:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  导师大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.23,0:03:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.95,0:03:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只龙是靠导师大人的力量抵挡住的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.51,0:03:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.41,0:04:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您太谦虚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导师大人  我有一个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.11,0:04:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为感谢  我想招待您进餐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以赏光吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔托洛卿  你想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  我不知道你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想尽力为导师大人消除疲劳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.54,0:04:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  我去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导师大人接受我的邀请了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导师大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎也能一起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  请停一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.98,0:05:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱菈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.90,0:05:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞迪雷克虽然还没完有完全被污染
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.49,0:05:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但时间也所剩无几了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.06,0:05:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.39,0:05:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得想想办法才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.79,0:05:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎殿下就那样呆着  我来送您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.56,0:05:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送我？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王陛下传话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.31,0:05:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请尽快前往王宫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.85,0:05:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没听说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在等着您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:05:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们似乎不想让艾莉莎同席
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷  抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.39,0:06:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.27,0:06:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么导师大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎您导师大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.92,0:06:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导师大人和艾莉莎公主是什么样的关系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.31,0:06:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.27,0:06:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然认识还没多久  但我觉得是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能和我成为朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.27,0:06:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想和我做朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是看不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来干杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.87,0:06:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷  不要轻易喝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很香…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  很美味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还和您胃口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是海兰德的特产
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因为最近连续灾害收成不是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.42,0:07:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么话要对我说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导师大人今后有什么打算吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.07,0:07:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们来说务必想借助导师大人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.82,0:07:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.11,0:07:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以告诉我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去追龙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追龙…想做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道我能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.61,0:07:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但龙是不详的象征的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里也许就会有改善世界的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.79,0:07:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时候不早了  今天就到这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷  我要去马林顿了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.77,0:08:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是国王陛下的亲令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是那个叫巴尔托洛的人搞的鬼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.03,0:08:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是即使是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.61,0:08:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不能对受疫病折磨的人们弃之不顾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.07,0:08:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吗  就那样放走了导师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要离开瑞迪雷克的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.44,0:08:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那现在也没有必要在这里流血
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么战争的准备呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然继续进行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.10,0:08:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱菈  可以谈谈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗  米克里欧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.92,0:08:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到今天的史雷我就在想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.98,0:09:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷成为了导师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.94,0:09:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在直视着他的命运前进
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得他成了遥不可及的存在了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.20,0:09:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢  我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.08,0:09:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么米克里欧今后打算怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.15,0:09:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不知道  虽然不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我觉得至今的关系将无法持续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.27,0:09:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷成了导师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我该做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.74,0:09:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然打算暂时和史雷一起旅行才离开了故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.05,0:09:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要回伊子集去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  虽然也有过这个念头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.87,0:09:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷如果今后要作为导师周游世界的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.13,0:09:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没办法丢下他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.38,0:10:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米克里欧真的很喜欢史雷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.80,0:10:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是孽缘而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米克里欧能为史雷做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.72,0:10:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱菈  马上去追米克里欧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.66,0:10:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到凭魔的话他一个人该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点事他应该明白的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.81,0:10:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么还一个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.48,0:10:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说米克里欧有他的理由才会一个人离开的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.06,0:10:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去追他了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.73,0:10:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.23,0:11:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了成为真正的导师我也有我该做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了瑞迪雷克之后一直向北走的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.72,0:11:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会到达一片很大的湖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.77,0:11:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有一座被称为「戈尔哈多」的遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.46,0:11:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那座遗迹里沉睡着可以镇魔的传说中的神器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.83,0:11:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神器？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.48,0:11:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我的圣剑是相同的东西  是圣遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.90,0:11:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米克里欧能得到那个的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能靠自己帮助史雷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.62,0:11:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这么认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.34,0:11:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要出发了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病情的发展可不等人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:12:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.16,0:12:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉这么晚才还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是米克里欧从遗迹捡回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  我真的很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.57,0:12:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是很重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.35,0:12:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷  如果可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到中途就行  可以来做我们的守卫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.89,0:12:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家第一次亲眼见到了龙的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说揭开了它的面纱成为了现实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.95,0:12:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在传说中有线索吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵峰雷弗尔克
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屡次在龙的传说中登场的人迹罕至的险峰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.67,0:12:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  我去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是长尾怪  只生活在这座森林里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.71,0:13:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有危险吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  是很温顺的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.48,0:13:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  是什么凭魔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.66,0:13:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是蛇还是蜥蜴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.47,0:14:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.19,0:14:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.41,0:14:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱菈大人真的不用吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.42,0:14:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么只喝点饮料也好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.51,0:14:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这附近结的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锉碎了以后用热水煮成的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.43,0:14:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好酸  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.21,0:14:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.23,0:14:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.92,0:14:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎  可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.38,0:14:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.95,0:14:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱菈大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.49,0:14:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  艾莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长尾怪竟然会袭击人类
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.58,0:15:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.28,0:15:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭魔！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.10,0:15:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再经过两座村子  渡过一条大河就是马林顿了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.42,0:15:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是个什么样的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.55,0:15:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人口仅次于瑞迪雷克  也是陪都
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.91,0:15:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化水准很高  识字率在国内最高
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经也是父亲引以为豪的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.40,0:15:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疫病的影响有那么严重吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.65,0:16:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是医师团  也不知道会有多大效果
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以谈谈史雷的话题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.54,0:16:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.75,0:16:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前听你说过没有离开过伊子集
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.08,0:16:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.39,0:16:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是婴儿的时候发生了一场大火
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷似乎从那里救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就一直在伊子集里生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.36,0:16:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然没能和他交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一定是一位了不起的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.24,0:16:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是被爷爷的加护保护着的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到下界才终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人类吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.65,0:16:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…你一开始就看得见天族吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么一说…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.79,0:16:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是看得见的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷说是因为一起生活才感知到天族的存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.01,0:16:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想多了解一些天族
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:16:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以告诉我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天遗见闻录里也写到过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.95,0:17:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太古时代  人类感知天族和他们共同生存
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.94,0:17:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天族们在不同的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.39,0:17:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化作土守护大地  化作风支撑天空
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.79,0:17:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化作水润泽河流  化作火维系生活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.24,0:17:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维持着它们的平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土  风  水  火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.72,0:17:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  天族也不是万能的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有擅长和不擅长的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱菈是火属性的天族
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.35,0:17:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米克里欧擅长操纵水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们却无法再感知到天族
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.77,0:17:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为这样么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.23,0:17:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才产生了这个灾难的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.72,0:17:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类忘记了对天族的崇敬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.21,0:17:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内心充满了怀疑  邪念以及争执
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.66,0:18:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也就是说灾难是人心所孕育的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这个世界充满了污秽是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.52,0:18:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无疑问灾难也正在扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.56,0:18:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想创造天族和人类能够共存的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷在伊子集是这么说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.86,0:18:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思议我记得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是因为史雷小时候起就和天族一起生活的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.20,0:18:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单身一人也不会寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.45,0:18:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很符合导师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.50,0:18:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来我从没感到过寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.90,0:18:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有大家在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.01,0:18:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有米克里欧在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.96,0:19:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱菈说得没错的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.58,0:19:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近应该会有遗迹的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.63,0:19:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不能输给他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.99,0:19:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越来越近了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.23,0:19:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是雷弗尔克
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.26,0:19:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是我赢了呢  史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是我赢了  米克里欧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.70,0:20:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的月亮真漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米克里欧也在哪里看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.18,0:20:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.28,0:22:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱菈  为什么愁眉苦脸的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.13,0:22:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.83,0:22:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我考虑了一下有关净化的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.23,0:22:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,净化么  很复杂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.39,0:22:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.17,0:22:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才刚成为导师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.50,0:23:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话也不知道能把这个世界净化成什么样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.87,0:23:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.17,0:23:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我想在旅行中锻炼作为导师的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.02,0:23:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽可能净化这个世上的污秽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.24,0:23:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷竟然也在考虑净化的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.48,0:23:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也算是导师  这是当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.92,0:23:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  莱菈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.27,0:23:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有灵感了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.06,0:23:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.99,0:23:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来净化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.85,0:23:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷  和米克里欧吵架也太冲动了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.90,0:23:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这很「净化」吧  锵锵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.31,0:23:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你考虑的是冷笑话啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.49,0:23:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周「灵峰雷弗尔克」  敬请期待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.46,0:23:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱菈  那女孩是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.92,0:01:06.44,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}向着遥远前方的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.66,0:01:08.74,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}你顺风而行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:16.62,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}追寻的答案不易找到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.80,0:01:20.99,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}从开始就已明白才跨出的一步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.53,0:01:30.49,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}梦想的足迹  无数次绕远路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.68,0:01:34.99,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}将描绘好的世界地图展开
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.03,0:01:38.50,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}回响吧！风之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.78,0:01:43.68,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}闭上眼睛  心中的声音鼓舞着我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.84,0:01:49.06,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}目的地还在更高的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.55,0:01:52.06,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}传递吧！风之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.26,0:01:57.17,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}侧耳倾听  心中的声音满溢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.33,0:02:02.39,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}释放出耀眼的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.65,0:02:06.16,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}你化为蓝色的旋律吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.79,0:20:59.64,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}此刻闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:07.55,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}在这不归的旅途上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:13.42,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}在片刻的安宁中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.62,0:21:19.94,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}我们怀着愿望入睡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.33,0:21:27.49,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}梦中的世界被光明照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.81,0:21:34.70,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}满溢的热情  寄宿着希望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.93,0:21:42.66,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}为了明天暂作休憩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.76,0:21:48.43,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}我们现在在这里欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.48,0:21:54.28,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}它将在这旅途的终点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.40,0:22:01.39,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}一定会抓住命运的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.61,0:22:07.35,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}在此时此处描绘着梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.44,0:22:12.36,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.42,0:22:19.10,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}共同前行
